{
  "stem": "7414.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You had to wait in the queue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we were in our hometown.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We had-- we knew people, young people, who were in the shops, and we could get from, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And behind that door, we had got so we did not need to stand in those queues so much.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then I have to go back and to tell that in meantime, I lost a grandmother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She died, peacefully, in 1914-- '40.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That was my father's mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She was nearly 100 years old then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then a little bit later, after all the family dispersed everywhere, my grandfather, my mother's father, died peacefully.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he was buried.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then my-- onto my grandmother, from my mother's mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This was alive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I took her in, because she was all alone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I took her to-- just to our-- those little two rooms.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When my mother came, so we were too crowded.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she found a room where she put my grandmother and my mother-in-law, my husband's mother, together, in the one room.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that-- now it is '41, and we are in our flat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I must tell that Przemysl was quiet till a whole year.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It means the first day we had to put on white band on our arm with a Magen David.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we lived in our flat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to observe the curfew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were not allowed to walk on the footpaths, for example.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to go out, always, in a group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- But it was still-- we had-- look, we had jewelry, which we did not sell.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we still had things which we could exchange with the peasant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The peasant came to the city-- to the town with some food, meat or butter or something.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
